chapters.title: Chapter 18:  An Offer
chapters.info: Setalle Anan, p. 380 (436)—Stately innkeeper of The Wandering Woman, the inn at which Mat and Olver stayed at in Ebou Dar. She has hazel eyes, marking her a non-native to Ebou Dar. She works closely with the Kin, and knew of their existance despite not being a part of it.
